name: pulumi-csharp-infra
description: Simple c# application with a ui and a backend api deployed on AWS EKS using pulumi to provision all infrastructure from ground up

name: fastapi-aws-app-runner
description: This repository provides a streamlined solution for deploying FastAPI applications, leveraging AWS App Runner for hassle-free scalability. With GitHub Actions, you can ensure your code is continuously integrated, tested, and deployed, saving you time and effort.

name: dask-ecs-lib
description: dask-ecs-lib is a Python library that effortlessly spins up a Dask cluster on AWS ECS using Fargate, allowing you to seamlessly execute and parallelize your functions.

name: FastEdgeSyncAI
description: FastEdgeSyncAI provides codes and datasets for a robust synchronizer tailored for AI tasks in edge computing environments. Accelerate your AI applications and ensure seamless synchronization.

name: FogSyncSimulator
description: FogSyncSimulator is a powerful tool that enables the simulation of synchronization scheduling in fog devices through clustering. Dive into the world of fog computing and fine-tune your scheduling algorithms for optimal performance.

name: SSOSolution-Keycloak
description: Single Sign-On (SSO) solution with Keycloak. Consolidated user authentication and access control across various applications to significantly enhancing security measures and user experiences.

name: aws-vpc-template-terraform
description: Simple VPC network module to create private and public subnets along with associated networking.
